#, python-brace-format
msgid "Mozilla Add-ons: {} [{}]"
msgstr "Mozilla dodaci: {} [{}]"

msgid "Email address"
msgstr "Adresa e-pošte"

msgid "Invalid email provided."
msgstr "Navedena e-pošta je neispravna."

msgid "Reason for appeal"
msgstr "Razlog za žalbu"

msgid ""
"Please explain why you believe that this decision was made in error, and/or "
"does not align with the applicable policy or law."
msgstr ""
"Objasnite zašto smatrate da je ova odluka doneta pogrešno i/ili da nije u "
"skladu sa važećom politikom ili zakonom."

msgid "User profile"
msgstr "Korisnički profil"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "\"{}\" for {}"
msgstr "\"{}\" za {}"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Please ensure this field has no more than {max_length} characters."
msgstr "Postarajte se da ovo polje ne sadrži više od {max_length} znakova."

msgid "Invalid value"
msgstr "Neispravna vrednost"

msgid "Appeal reviewer decision"
msgstr "Uložite žalbu na odluku proveravača"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Decision {0}"
msgstr "Odluka {0}"

msgid "Thank you. Your appeal has been recorded."
msgstr "Hvala vam. Vaša žalba je primljena."

msgid "OK"
msgstr "U redu"

msgid "Thank you for your report."
msgstr "Hvala vam na izveštaju."

msgid ""
"We have already reviewed a similar appeal from another reporter, and have "
"reversed our prior decision. We have taken action against the content and/or "
"account holder in accordance with our policies."
msgstr ""
"Već smo razmotrili sličnu žalbu drugog prijavljivača i opozvali smo našu "
"prethodnu odluku. Preduzeli smo radnju protiv sadržaja i/ili vlasnika naloga "
"u skladu sa našim polisama."

msgid ""
"Because the decision you are appealing has already been overturned, your "
"appeal will not be processed."
msgstr ""
"Pošto je odluka protiv koje se žalite već poništena, vaša žalba neće biti "
"obrađena."

msgid ""
"The decision you are appealing has already been overridden by a new "
"decision, so this decision can't be appealed."
msgstr ""
"Odluka protiv koje se žalite već je zamenjena novom odlukom, tako da se "
"protiv ove odluke ne može žaliti."

msgid "This decision can't be appealed."
msgstr "Protiv ove odluke se ne može žaliti."

msgid "Hello,"
msgstr "Zdravo,"

msgid "Mozilla Add-ons Team"
msgstr "Tim za Mozilla-ine dodatke"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Thank you for your report about %(name)s on Mozilla Add-ons, and for "
"providing more information about your concerns.\n"
"\n"
"After reviewing your appeal, we determined that the previous decision, that "
"this content does not violate Mozilla’s policies (%(policy_document_url)s), "
"was correct. Based on that determination, we have denied your appeal, and "
"will not take any action against the account or the content.\n"
"%(manual_reasoning_text)s.\n"
"\n"
"Thank you for your attention.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Zahvaljujemo vam na prijavi za %(name)s na Mozilla-inim dodacima, kao i na "
"pružanju dodatnih informacija o vašim zabrinutostima.\n"
"\n"
"Nakon razmatranja vaše žalbe, utvrdili smo da je prethodna odluka, da ovaj "
"sadržaj ne krši Mozilla-ine politike (%(policy_document_url)s), bila "
"ispravna. Na osnovu tog utvrđenja, odbili smo vašu žalbu i nećemo preduzeti "
"ikakve radnje protiv naloga ili sadržaja.\n"
"%(manual_reasoning_text)s.\n"
"\n"
"Hvala vam na pažnji.\n"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Thank you for your report about %(name)s on Mozilla Add-ons, and for "
"providing more information about your concerns.\n"
"\n"
"After reviewing your appeal, we have determined that our prior decision, "
"that this content does not violate Mozilla's policies "
"(%(policy_document_url)s), was incorrect. Based on that determination, we "
"have removed the content, and notified the user of our action.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Zahvaljujemo vam na prijavi za %(name)s na Mozilla-inim dodacima, kao i na "
"pružanju dodatnih informacija o vašim zabrinutostima.\n"
"\n"
"Nakon razmatranja vaše žalbe, utvrdili smo da je naša prethodna odluka, da "
"ovaj sadržaj ne krši Mozilla-ine politike (%(policy_document_url)s), bila "
"pogrešna. Na osnovu tog utvrđenja, uklonili smo sadržaj i obavestili "
"korisnika o našoj radnji.\n"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Thank you for your report about %(name)s on Mozilla Add-ons, and for "
"providing more information about your concerns.\n"
"\n"
"After reviewing your appeal, we have determined that our prior decision, "
"that this content does not violate Mozilla's policies "
"(%(policy_document_url)s), was incorrect. Based on that determination, we "
"have requested the developer make changes. If they do not update their "
"content to correct the violation, we will remove it.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Zahvaljujemo vam na prijavi za %(name)s na Mozilla-inim dodacima, kao i na "
"pružanju dodatnih informacija o vašim zabrinutostima.\n"
"\n"
"Nakon razmatranja vaše žalbe, utvrdili smo da je naša prethodna odluka, da "
"ovaj sadržaj ne krši Mozilla-ine politike (%(policy_document_url)s), bila "
"pogrešna. Na osnovu tog utvrđenja, zatražili smo od programera da izvrši "
"izmene. Ako programer ne ažurira svoj sadržaj kako bi ispravio kršenje, "
"uklonićemo ga.\n"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Thank you for your report about %(name)s, at %(target_url)s.\n"
"\n"
"We reviewed your report and the content in question, and found that it does "
"not violate Mozilla's policies (%(policy_document_url)s).  It will therefore "
"not be subject to any moderation action.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Zahvaljujemo vam na prijavi za %(name)s na adresi %(target_url)s.\n"
"\n"
"Pregledali smo vašu prijavu i pomenuti sadržaj i utvrdili smo da on ne krši "
"Mozilla-ine politike (%(policy_document_url)s). Stoga, on neće biti predmet "
"ikakvih radnji moderiranja.\n"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"You have the right to appeal this decision within 6 months from the date of "
"this email. See %(appeal_url)s for details on the appeal process, including "
"how to file an appeal for this specific decision."
msgstr ""
"Imate pravo na žalbu protiv ove odluke u roku od 6 meseci od datuma ove e-"
"pošte. Pogledajte %(appeal_url)s za detalje o procesu žalbe, uključujući i "
"to kako da podnesete žalbu protiv ove konkretne odluke."

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Thank you for your report about the following add-on on Mozilla Add-ons: "
"%(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"We reviewed your report and the content in question, and found that it "
"violates Mozilla's policies (%(policy_document_url)s), and have therefore "
"removed the content.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Hvala vam na prijavi sledećeg dodatka na Mozilla-inim dodacima: %(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"Pregledali smo vašu prijavu i sporni sadržaj i utvrdili smo da on krši "
"Mozilla-ine politike (%(policy_document_url)s), te smo zbog toga uklonili "
"sadržaj.\n"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Thank you for your report about the following add-on on Mozilla Add-ons: "
"%(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"We reviewed your report and the content in question, and found that it "
"violates Mozilla's policies (%(policy_document_url)s), and have therefore "
"requested the developer make changes. If they do not update their content to "
"correct the violation, we will remove it.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Hvala vam na prijavi sledećeg dodatka na Mozilla-inim dodacima: %(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"Pregledali smo vašu prijavu i sporni sadržaj i utvrdili smo da on krši "
"Mozilla-ine politike (%(policy_document_url)s), te smo zbog toga zatražili "
"od programera da unese izmene. Ako on ne ažurira svoj sadržaj kako bi "
"ispravio kršenje, uklonićemo ga.\n"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Thank you for your report about the following collection on Mozilla Add-ons: "
"%(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"We reviewed your report and the content in question, and found that it "
"violates Mozilla's policies (%(policy_document_url)s), and have therefore "
"removed the content.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Hvala vam na prijavi sledeće zbirke na Mozilla-inim dodacima: %(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"Pregledali smo vašu prijavu i sporni sadržaj i utvrdili smo da on krši "
"Mozilla-ine politike (%(policy_document_url)s), te smo zbog toga uklonili "
"sadržaj.\n"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Thank you for your report about the following rating on Mozilla Add-ons: "
"%(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"We reviewed your report and the content in question, and found that it "
"violates Mozilla's policies (%(policy_document_url)s), and have therefore "
"removed the content.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Hvala vam na prijavi sledeće ocene na Mozilla-inim dodacima: %(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"Pregledali smo vašu prijavu i sporni sadržaj i utvrdili smo da on krši "
"Mozilla-ine politike (%(policy_document_url)s), te smo zbog toga uklonili "
"sadržaj.\n"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Thank you for your report about the following user profile on Mozilla Add-"
"ons: %(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"We reviewed your report and the content in question, and found that it "
"violates Mozilla's policies (%(policy_document_url)s), and have therefore "
"removed the content.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Hvala vam na prijavi sledećeg korisničkog profila na Mozilla-inim dodacima: "
"%(name)s.\n"
"\n"
"Pregledali smo vašu prijavu i sporni sadržaj i utvrdili da on krši Mozilla-"
"ine politike (%(policy_document_url)s), te smo zbog toga uklonili sadržaj.\n"

