msgid "CIDR"
msgstr "CIDR"

msgid ""
"Some features are temporarily disabled while we perform website maintenance. "
"We'll be back to full capacity shortly."
msgstr ""
"Neke funkcije su privremeno onemogućene dok vršimo održavanje veb stranice. "
"Vratićemo se u punom kapacitetu uskoro."

msgid "This name cannot be used."
msgstr "Ovo ime ne može da se koristi."

msgid "URLs are not allowed."
msgstr "URL-ovi nisu dozvoljeni."

msgid "Must contain at least one printable character."
msgstr "Mora sadržati najmanje jedan štampabilni znak."

msgid "Ensure this field contains at least one letter or number character."
msgstr "Ubedite se da ovo polje sadrži najmanje jedno slovo ili cifru."

#, python-format
msgid ""
"This field can only be used to link to external websites. URLs on %(domain)s "
"are not allowed."
msgstr ""
"Ovo polje se može koristiti samo za povezivanje sa spoljnim veb stranicama. "
"URL-ovi na %(domain)s nisu dozvoljeni."

msgid "Not allowed"
msgstr "Nije dozvoljeno"

msgid "Oops! Not allowed."
msgstr "Ups! Nije dozvoljeno."

msgid "You tried to do something that you weren't allowed to."
msgstr "Pokušali ste da uradite nešto što nije dozvoljeno."

msgid ""
"You are seeing this message because this HTTPS site requires a 'Referer "
"header' to be sent by your Web browser, but none was sent. This header is "
"required for security reasons, to ensure that your browser is not being "
"hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Vidite ovu poruku zato što ova HTTPS stranica zahteva da vaš veb pregledač "
"pošalje 'Referer zaglavlje', ali takvo zaglavlje nije poslato. Ovo zaglavlje "
"je potrebno radi bezbednosti, kako bi se osiguralo da treće lica ne preuzmu "
"kontrolu nad vašim pregledačom."

msgid ""
"If you have configured your browser to disable 'Referer' headers, please re-"
"enable them, at least for this site, or for HTTPS connections, or for 'same-"
"origin' requests."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste u vašem pregledaču podesili da onemogućite 'Referer' zaglavlja, "
"ponovo ih omogućite, barem za ovu stranicu, ili za HTTPS veze, ili za 'same-"
"origin' zahteve."

msgid ""
"You are seeing this message because this site requires a CSRF cookie when "
"submitting forms. This cookie is required for security reasons, to ensure "
"that your browser is not being hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Vidite ovu poruku zato što ova stranica zahteva CSRF kolačić pri slanju "
"obrazaca. Ovaj kolačić je potreban iz razloga bezbednosti, kako bi se "
"osiguralo da treće strane ne preuzmu kontrolu nad vašim pregledačem."

msgid "Not Found"
msgstr "Nije pronađeno"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"<h1>We're sorry, but we can't find what you're looking for.</h1> <p> The "
"page or file you requested wasn't found on our site. It's possible that you "
"clicked a link that's out of date, or typed in the address incorrectly. </p> "
"<ul> <li>If you typed in the address, please double check the spelling.</li> "
"<li> If you followed a link from somewhere, please %(open_bug_link)sfile an "
"issue%(close_bug_link)s. Tell us where you came from and what you were "
"looking for, and we'll do our best to fix it. </li> </ul> <p>Or you can just "
"jump over to some of the popular pages on our website.</p> <ul> <li>Are you "
"interested in a <a href=\"%(rec)s\">list of featured add-ons</a>?</li> <li> "
"Do you want to <a href=\"%(search)s\">search for add-ons</a>? You may go to "
"the <a href=\"%(search)s\">search page</a> or just use the search field "
"above. </li> <li> If you prefer to start over, just go to the <a "
"href=\"%(home)s\">add-ons front page</a>. </li> </ul>"
msgstr ""
"<h1>Žao nam je, ali ne možemo naći ono što tražite.</h1> <p> Stranica ili "
"datoteka koju ste zahtevali nije pronađena na našoj veb stranici. Moguće je "
"da ste kliknuli na zastarelu vezu ili ste pogrešno uneli adresu. </p> <ul> "
"<li>Ako ste uneli adresu, proverite da li je pravilno napisana.</li> <li> "
"Ako ste pratili vezu sa nekog drugog mesta, %(open_bug_link)sprijavite "
"problem%(close_bug_link)s. Recite nam odakle ste došli i šta ste tražili, a "
"mi ćemo se postarati da to popravimo. </li> </ul> <p>Ili možete jednostavno "
