msgid ""
"Download Firefox extensions that can help download web, music and video "
"content. You can also find extensions to manage downloads, share files, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatke koji vam mogu pomoći u preuzimanju veb sadržaja, "
"muzike i videa. Takođe možete pronaći dodatke za upravljanje preuzimanjima, "
"deljenje datoteka i još mnogo toga."

msgid "Feeds, News & Blogging"
