msgid ""
"Download Firefox extensions that remove clutter so you can stay up-to-date "
"on social media, catch up on blogs, RSS feeds, reduce eye strain, and more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatke koji uklanjaju suvišne elemente kako biste ostali "
"u toku sa društvenim mrežama, pratili blogove, RSS izvore, umanjili zamor "
"očiju i još mnogo toga."

