msgstr "Fotografije, muzika i video snimci"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox extensions that enhance photo, music and video experiences. "
"Extensions in this category modify audio and video, reverse image search, "
"and more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatke koji poboljšaju iskustvo sa fotografijama, muzikom "
"i videima. Dodaci u ovoj kategoriji izmenjaju zvuk i video, omogućavaju "
"obrnutu pretragu slika i još mnogo toga."

#. editorial content for the secondary hero shelves.
msgid "Privacy & Security"
msgstr "Privatnost i bezbednost"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox extensions to browse privately and securely. This category "
"includes extensions to block annoying ads, prevent tracking, manage "
"redirects, and more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatke kako biste pregledali veb stranice privatno i "
"bezbedno. Ova kategorija uključuje dodatke koji blokiraju dosadne oglase, "
"sprečavaju praćenje, upravljaju preusmerenjima i još mnogo toga."

msgid "Search Tools"
msgstr "Alatke za pretraživanje"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox extensions for search and look-up. This category includes "
"extensions that highlight and search text, lookup IP addresses/domains, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatke za pretragu i traženje. Ova kategorija uključuje "
"dodatke koji ističu i pretražuju tekst, traže IP adrese/domene i još mnogo "
"toga."

msgid "Shopping"
msgstr "Kupovina"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox extensions that can enhance your online shopping experience "
"with coupon finders, deal finders, review analyzers, more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatke koji mogu poboljšati vaše iskustvo onlajn kupovine "
"pomoću alata za pronalaženje kupona, pronalaženja ponuda, analizatora "
"recenzija i još mnogo toga."

msgid "Social & Communication"
msgstr "Društveno i komunikacija"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox extensions to enhance social media and instant messaging. "
"This category includes improved tab notifications, video downloaders, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatke za poboljšanje društvenih mreža i trenutne razmene "
"poruka. Ova kategorija uključuje poboljšana obaveštenja na jezičkima, "
"programe za preuzimanje videa i još mnogo toga."

msgid "Tabs"
msgstr "Jezičci"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox extension to customize tabs and the new tab page. Discover "
"extensions that can control tabs, change the way you interact with them, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatak za prilagođavanje jezička i stranice novog "
"jezička. Otkrijte dodatke koji mogu da upravljaju jezičkima, promene način "
"na koji sa njima interagujete i još mnogo toga."

msgid "Web Development"
msgstr "Veb programiranje"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox extensions that feature web development tools. This "
"category includes extensions for GitHub, user agent switching, cookie "
"management, and more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatke sa alatima za veb razvoj. Ova kategorija uključuje "
"dodatke za GitHub, promenu korisničkog zastupnika, upravljanje kolačićima i "
"još mnogo toga."

msgid "Other"
msgstr "Drugo"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox extensions that can be unpredictable and creative, yet "
"useful for those odd tasks."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox dodatke koji mogu biti nepredvidivi i kreativni, a ipak "
"korisni za neke neobične zadaće."

msgid "Abstract"
msgstr "Apstraktno"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox artistic and conceptual themes. This category includes "
"colorful palettes and shapes, fantasy landscapes, playful cats, psychedelic "
"flowers."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite umetničke i konceptualne teme za Firefox. Ova kategorija uključuje "
"šarene palete i oblike, fantastične pejzaže, razigrane mačke i psihodeličko "
"cveće."

msgid "Causes"
msgstr "Uzroci"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes for niche interests and topics. This category "
"includes sports themes, holidays, philanthropic causes, nationalities, and "
"much more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme za specifična interesovanja i teme. Ova kategorija "
"uključuje sportske teme, praznike, filantropske svrhe, nacionalnosti i još "
"mnogo toga."

msgid "Fashion"
msgstr "Moda"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes that celebrate style of all forms—patterns, florals, "
"textures, models, and more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme koje slave stil svih oblika - šare, cvetne motive, "
"teksture, modele i još mnogo toga."

msgid "Film and TV"
msgstr "Film i TV"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes with movies and television. This category includes "
"anime like Uchiha Madara, movies like The Matrix, shows (Game of Thrones), "
"and more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme sa filmovima i televizijom. Ova kategorija uključuje "
"anime kao što je Uchiha Madara, filmove kao što je The Matrix, emisije (Game "
"of Thrones) i još mnogo toga."

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes with the Firefox browser theme. This category "
"includes colorful, diverse depictions of the Firefox logo, including more "
"general fox themes."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme sa temom Firefox pregledača. Ova kategorija uključuje "
"šarene i raznovrsne prikaze Firefox logotipa, uključujući i opšte teme sa "
"lisicom."

msgid "Foxkeh"
msgstr "Fokskeh"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes with the Japanese Firefox. This category includes "
"themes that depict the cute Foxkeh mascot in various poses on diverse "
"landscapes."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme sa japanskim Firefox-om. Ova kategorija uključuje "
"teme koje prikazuju slatku maskotu Foxkeh u raznim pozama na raznovrsnim "
"pejzažima."

msgid "Holiday"
msgstr "Praznik"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes with holidays. This category includes Christmas, "
"Halloween, Thanksgiving, St. Patrick’s Day, Easter, Fourth of July, and more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme sa praznicima. Ova kategorija uključuje Božić, Noć "
"veštica, Dan zahvalnosti, Sveti Patrikov dan, Uskrs, Četvrti jul i još mnogo "
"toga."

msgid "Music"
msgstr "Muzika"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes for musical interests and artists. This category "
"includes popular bands like Nirvana and BTS, instruments, music videos, and "
"much more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme za muzička interesovanja i umetnike. Ova kategorija "
"uključuje popularne grupe kao što su Nirvana i BTS, instrumente, muzičke "
"spotove i još mnogo toga."

msgid "Nature"
msgstr "Priroda"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes with animals and natural landscapes. This category "
"includes flowers, sunsets, foxes, seasons, planets, kittens, birds, and more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme sa životinjama i prirodnim pejzažima. Ova kategorija "
"uključuje cveće, zalaske sunca, lisice, godinje vremena, planete, mačete, "
"ptice i još mnogo toga."

msgid "Download Firefox themes that are interesting, creative, and unique."
msgstr "Preuzmite Firefox teme koje su zanimljive, kreativne i jedinstvene."

msgid "Scenery"
msgstr "Pejzaž"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes that feature the environment and the natural world. "
"This category includes sunsets, beaches, illustrations, city skylines, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme koje prikazuju okruženje i prirodni svet. Ova "
"kategorija uključuje zalaske sunca, plaže, ilustracije, gradske siluete i "
"još mnogo toga."

msgid "Seasonal"
msgstr "Sezonski"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes for all four seasons—fall, winter, spring, and "
"summer. Autumn leaves, snowy mountain peaks, sunny summer days, and spring "
"flowers."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme za sva četiri godinja doba - jesen, zimu, proleće i "
"leto. Jeseno lišće, snežni vrhovi planina, sunčani letnji dani i prolećno "
"cveće."

msgid "Solid"
msgstr "Jednobojno"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes with solid and gradient colors to personalize your "
"browser. This category includes bold reds, pastels, soft greys, and much "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme sa punim bojama i prelivima da biste prilagodili svoj "
"pregledač. Ova kategorija uključuje jake crvene, pastelne boje, nežne sive i "
"još mnogo toga."

msgid "Sports"
msgstr "Sport"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes that feature a variety of sports. This category "
"includes country flags, sports teams, soccer, hockey, and more."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme koje prikazuju razne vrste sporta. Ova kategorija "
"uključuje državne zastavice, sportske ekipe, fudbal, hokej i još mnogo toga."

msgid "Websites"
msgstr "Veb stranice"

msgid ""
"Download Firefox themes that capture the essence of the web—captivating, "
"unusual, and distinctive."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Firefox teme koje dočaravaju suštinu veba - očaravajuće, neobične "
"i prepoznatljive."

