msgstr "Da"

msgid "No"
msgstr "Ne"

msgid "You have not uploaded a source file."
msgstr "Niste otpremili izvornu datoteku."

msgid "Source file uploaded but you indicated no source was needed."
msgstr ""
"Izvorna datoteka je otpremljena, ali ste naveli da izvor nije potreban."

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Ensure name and summary combined are at most {limit_value} characters (they "
"have {show_value})."
msgstr ""
"Uverete se da naziv i sažetak zajedno imaju najviše {limit_value} znakova "
"(trenutno imaju {show_value})."

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"On this site. <span class=\"helptext\">Your submission is publicly listed on "
"{site_domain}.</span>"
msgstr ""
"Na ovoj stranici. <span class=\"helptext\">Vaša prijava je javno navedena na "
"{site_domain}.</span>"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"On your own. <span class=\"helptext\">After your submission is signed by "
"Mozilla, you can download the .xpi file from the Developer Hub and "
"distribute it to your audience. Please make sure the add-on manifest’s <a "
"{a_attrs}>update_url</a> is provided, as this is the URL where Firefox finds "
"updates for automatic deployment to your users.</span>"
msgstr ""
"Samostalno. <span class=\"helptext\">Nakon što Mozilla potpiše vašu prijavu, "
"možete preuzmeti .xpi datoteku iz Centra za programera i raspodeliti je "
"svojoj publici. Uverete se da je <a {a_attrs}>update_url</a> u manifestu "
"dodatka naveden, jer je to URL na kojem Firefox pronalazi ažuriranja za "
"samostalno instaliranje vašim korisnicima.</span>"

