msgstr ""
"Da li ste sigurni da želite da uklonite sve <b>{0}</b> prevode? Ovo se ne "
"može poništiti."

msgid "Delete Locale"
msgstr "Obriši lokalitet"

msgid "No user with that email."
msgstr "Nema korisnika sa tom adresom e-pošte."

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Firefox user {id}"
msgstr "Firefox korisnik {id}"

msgid ""
"Multiple submissions violating our policies have been sent from your "
"location. The IP address has been blocked."
msgstr ""
"Višestruke prijave koje krše naša pravila poslate su sa vaše lokacije. IP "
"adresa je blokirana."

msgid "The email address used for your account is not allowed for submissions."
msgstr "E-pošta koja se koristi za vaš nalog nije dozvoljena za prijave."

msgid "The software or device you are using is not allowed for submissions."
msgstr "Program ili uređaj koji koristite nije dozvoljen za prijave."

msgid ""
"Before starting, please read and accept our Firefox Add-on Distribution "
"Agreement as well as our Review Policies and Rules. The Firefox Add-on "
"Distribution Agreement also links to our Privacy Notice which explains how "
"we handle your information."
msgstr ""
"Pre početka, pročitajte i prihvatite naš Ugovor o raspodeli Firefox-ovih "
"dodataka kao i naše polise i pravila recenzije. Ugovor o raspodeli Firefox-"
"ovih dodataka takođe sadrži vezu do našeg obaveštenja o privatnosti u kojem "
"je objašnjeno kako obrađujemo vaše podatke."

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Please read and accept our Firefox Add-on Distribution Agreement as well as "
"our Review Policies and Rules by visiting {url}"
msgstr ""
"Pročitajte i prihvatite naš Ugovor o raspodeli Firefox-ovih dodataka kao i "
"naše Polise i pravila recenzije tako što ćete posetiti {url}"

msgid "an add-on developer replies to my review"
msgstr "programer dodatka odgovara na moju recenziju"

msgid "new add-ons or Firefox features are available"
msgstr "novi dodaci ili Firefox mogućnosti su dostupni"

msgid "my add-on's compatibility is upgraded successfully"
msgstr "usaglašenost mog dodatka je uspešno nadograđena"

msgid "someone writes a review of my add-on"
msgstr "neko piše recenziju na moj dodatak"

msgid ""
"stay up-to-date with news and events relevant to add-on developers "
"(including the about:addons newsletter)"
msgstr ""
"ostanite u toku sa vestima i događajima relevantnim za programere dodataka "
"(uključujući bilten about:addons)"

msgid "my add-on's compatibility cannot be upgraded"
msgstr "usaglašenost mog dodatka se ne može nadograditi"

msgid "my add-on is reviewed by a reviewer"
msgstr "moj dodatak je pregledao recenzent"

msgid "Mozilla needs to contact me about my individual add-on"
msgstr "Mozilla treba da me kontaktira u vezi mog ličnog dodatka"

msgid "User Notifications"
msgstr "Obaveštenja korisnika"

msgid "An author has been added to your add-on"
msgstr "Autor je dodat Vašem dodatku"

msgid "An author role has been changed on your add-on"
msgstr "Uloga autora je promenjena na vašem dodatku"

msgid "An author has been removed from your add-on"
msgstr "Autor je uklonjen sa Vašeg dodatka"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"The following author has been added to your add-on %(addon_name)s "
"( %(addon_url)s ):\n"
"\n"
"%(author_name)s ( %(author_url)s ): %(author_role)s"
msgstr ""
"Sledeći autor je dodat vašem dodatku %(addon_name)s ( %(addon_url)s ):\n"
"\n"
"%(author_name)s ( %(author_url)s ): %(author_role)s"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"Greetings %(author_name)s,\n"
"\n"
"You have been invited to become an author of %(addon_name)s on %(domain)s. "
"Accepting the invitation will give you access to edit the add-on, and may "
"show your name in the authors list on the website.\n"
"\n"
"Click on the link below to respond if you want to be added as an author for "
"%(addon_name)s.\n"
"\n"
"%(author_confirmation_link)s\n"
"\n"
"Kind regards,\n"
"The Mozilla Add-ons Team"
msgstr ""
"Pozdrav, %(author_name)s,\n"
"\n"
"Pozvani ste da postanete autor dodatka %(addon_name)s na domenu %(domain)s. "
"Prihvatanjem poziva dobićete pristup za uređivanje dodatka, a vaše ime može "
"se pojaviti na spisku autora na veb stranici.\n"
"\n"
"Kliknite na vezu ispod da odgovorite ako želite da budete dodati kao autor "
"za %(addon_name)s.\n"
"\n"
"%(author_confirmation_link)s\n"
"\n"
"Srdačan pozdrav,\n"
"Tim za Mozilla dodatke"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"The following author has been changed on your add-on %(addon_name)s "
"( %(addon_url)s ):\n"
"\n"
"%(author_name)s ( %(author_url)s ): %(author_role)s"
msgstr ""
"Sledeći autor je izmenjen u vašem dodatku %(addon_name)s ( %(addon_url)s ):\n"
"\n"
"%(author_name)s ( %(author_url)s ): %(author_role)s"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"The following author has been removed from add-on %(addon_name)s "
"( %(addon_url)s ):\n"
"\n"
"%(author_name)s ( %(author_url)s )"
msgstr ""
"Sledeći autor je uklonjen iz dodatka %(addon_name)s ( %(addon_url)s ):\n"
"\n"
"%(author_name)s ( %(author_url)s )"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"You’re receiving this message because your user account %(name)s on "
"%(site_url)s has been deleted. This could have been done automatically if "
"you recently deleted your Mozilla account.\n"
"\n"
"Regards,\n"
"\n"
"Mozilla Add-ons Team"
msgstr ""
"Zdravo,\n"
"\n"
"Primate ovu poruku zato što je vaš korisnički nalog %(name)s na %(site_url)s "
"obrisan. To se moglo desiti samostalno ako ste nedavno obrisali svoj Mozilla "
"nalog.\n"
"\n"
"S poštovanjem,\n"
"\n"
"Mozilla Add-ons tim"

#, python-format
msgid "Delay-rejected, scheduled for %s"
msgstr "Odbijeno sa odlaganjem, zakazano za %s"

msgid "Auto-approved, Confirmed"
msgstr "Automatski odobreno, potvrđeno"

msgid "Auto-approved, not Confirmed"
msgstr "Samostalno odobreno, nije potvrđeno"

msgid "Approved, Manual"
msgstr "Odobreno, ručno"

msgid "Disabled by Developer"
msgstr "Onemogućeno programerom"

